                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d555">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.515/80: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hibbard</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Monrovia</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-10-30T16:00:00-00:44"
                            >October 30, 1942—4 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received October 31—8:46 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>367. Department’s confidential telegram No. 236, September 26, 2 p.m. The
                    following Executive Order has been signed by President Barclay and will be
                    published on November 2: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“It is hereby ordered that on and after November 1, 1942 lawful metallic
                            currency of the United States of America and lawful currency notes of
                            the United States of America, of denominations not exceeding $20, shall
                            be legal tender for the payment of all private and public obligations,
                            at the rate of $4 (United States) to the British pound now in
                            circulation in Liberia or $4 (United States) to $4.80 Liberian silver
                            and alloy currency.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hibbard</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
